data.description: Experience comfortable living in this spacious 1,754 square foot townhome, featuring three large bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, and a huge family room with a balcony that offers stunning valley and lake views. Practicality meets ease with a two-car garage, ample storage, and low HOA fees that include internet service. Feature amenities include a private park, and the benefit of no yard work, making this an ideal home for those seeking convenience and natural beauty. Minutes to American Fork Canyon and walking distance to hiking, biking trails and the golf course. ***Note: Back on the market. Buyers cancelled due to personal reasons. Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from last MLS .  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
